         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility"> ¶ Hamburg, 8 March ¶  ¶ 1855 ¶ Most esteemed Professor, ¶  ¶ I hope that you will have received my last letter, which accompanied the manuscript of Mueller's Algae. Today I have the pleasure to send ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">M55.03.08</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Wilhelm Sonder to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Diederich von Schlechtendal</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">MS not seen; text given here extracted from Tkach, Neubauer &amp; Roser (2022), Brief</seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">26</seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>Hamburg d. 8<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont">ä</seg>r<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>55</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Geehrtester Herr!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich hoffe, dass Sie meinen letzten Brief, welchen das Manuskript der Müller’schen Algen<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>begleitete, erhalten haben werden. Heute habe ich das Vergnügen, einen Theil der Leguminosen<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>zu übersenden. Bentham bittet, falls sich lateinische Schnitzer in seiner Arbeit finden sollten, solche gefälligst zu ändern.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>—<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Ich hoffe Ihnen bald mehr zum Drucke übersenden zu können.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>—<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Zwei kleine Kisten mit Pflanzen u dergl.<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>ist schon wieder in England angekommen, mit dem ersten Schiffe erwarte ich sie, dabei sind auch Rapporte<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>über Müller’s letzte Reisen. Müller hat mir neulich aus dem Innern<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>geschrieben, er hatte im Novbr. den hohen Mount Wellington<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>bestiegen und manches Schöne gefunden. Ende dieses Monats geht ein Schiff nach Melbourne ab, womit ich Sachen schicke. Vielleicht erhalte ich bis dahin Abdrucke der Kryptogamen.<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>Hampe hat sich schon wegen der Moose erkundigt.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sollten Sie Ihren dortigen Antiquar<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>nicht veranlassen können, mir recht bald ein Verzeichniss<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>seiner botanischen Bücher zu senden, ich möchte für Dr. Müller<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>noch einiges kaufen, namentlich wäre es mir lieb, den Labillardière (Plant. Nov. Hollandiae) zu erstehen.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Wie ich höre, besitzen Sie das Herbarium Ihres Vaters,<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>der viele Pflanzen von Thunberg besass. Sollte sich in der Sammlung die Penaea tomentosa<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>befinden, so würden Sie mich verpflichten, wenn Sie mir die Pflanze auf einige Tage leihen wollten.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Hochachtungsvoll</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihr</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>ergebener</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hamburg, 8 March<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1855</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Most esteemed Professor,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I hope that you will have received my last letter, which accompanied the manuscript of Mueller's Algae. Today I have the pleasure to send a part of the legumes. Bentham asks me if any Latin mistakes should be found in his work, to kindly change them.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>—<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I hope to be able to send you more for printing soon.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>—<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Two small boxes with plants and the like have already arrived again<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in England, I expect them with the first ship, with them are also reports on Mueller's last journeys. Mueller recently wrote to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>me from<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the interior, saying that he had climbed the high Mount Wellington in November and found many beautiful things.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>A ship is leaving for Melbourne at the end of this month and I am sending things on it. Perhaps I will receive<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>reprints of the cryptogams by then. Hampe has already enquired about the mosses.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>If you cannot arrange for your antiquarian bookseller there to send me a<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>list of his botanical books very soon, I would still like to buy some<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>things<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for Dr Mueller, in particular I would like to purchase the Labillardière (Plant. Nov. Hollandiae).<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I understand that you own your father's herbarium, which contained many of Thunberg's plants.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Should<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Penaea tomentosa</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>be<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in the collection, you would oblige me if you would lend me the plant for a few days.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>devoted</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder</p>
         </div>
      </body>
